Latest: Carrasco to miss tomorrow&rsquo;s game versus Tianjin and may not play another game for Dalian for a long time according to head coach Cui Kangxi.<br />
<br />
Cui Kangxi: &ldquo;Carrasco kept saying he wants to move to Europe. He repeated that many times during the season. I read the latest quotes from his agent. No one promised to let him leave. No one guaranteed him that.&rdquo;

